{"tid":696073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"深夜叫下春","createTime":"2018-06-09T17:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T21:23:56.000Z","uid":167219,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e389de7e2e08f03688e1f4790fda8891624769d5","tid":696073,"uid":167219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T17:54:21.000Z","msg":"從何時你也學會不要離群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己唔離群但覺得個群離我越黎越遠<br />\n以前明明好開心<br />\n雖然成日俾人笑俾人蝦<br />\n但生日會有人記得會俾驚喜我<br />\n宜家冇lu<br />\n大家記得新既人就忘記左舊既人<br />\n以前唔會咁小圈子<br />\n有咩都想大家一齊玩<br />\n宜家又冇lu<br />\n小圈子一個個<br />\n但係都要扮哂close攬頭攬頸咁<br />\n曬到仆街仲要咁辛苦做野<br />\n同伴既你地去睇其他人去俾水其他人冇理過我<br />\n飲啖水都要對家但一齊做野既人施捨俾我<br />\n好攰啦<br />\n但冇用<br />\n好鍾意呢個地方一直想留低<br />\n但個心真係好辛苦<br />\n點解仲要勉強自己笑呀點解？<br />\n連影相我都唔想行埋去啦<br />\nSorry其實係訓唔著叫下春<br />\n想叫春就一齊叫下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a19bddaaf9dc8702c488dec07487ab23ad10ee8","tid":696073,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bccfab002d1e099e493e47f0568b194afeec68","tid":696073,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a19bddaaf9dc8702c488dec07487ab23ad10ee8","tid":696073,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec4fd5128170fa8968392400b69eeecdb8036af","tid":696073,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018